title: Bump sha2 from 0.9.6 to 0.9.8

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [sha2](https://github.com/RustCrypto/hashes) from 0.9.6 to 0.9.8.
Commits

  • 93d895d sha2: Fix bug in the AVX2 backend (#314)

  • efda00d Add x86 intrinsics support for sha2-512 (#312)
